data.description: Welcome to this stunning residence nestled in the Morse Valley neighborhood of Copperas Cove! This recently updated two-story home sits on a generous corner lot, and offers an abundance of open space and modern comforts. As you step inside, you will be greeted by the inviting living area with its sizable layout, high ceilings, and a charming wood burning fireplace. Your expansive, beautifully appointed kitchen features a center island, modern appliances, and ample cabinetry for storage. The spacious master suite is complete with a luxurious ensuite bathroom. It boasts a soaker tub, double vanity, and separate shower for a spa-like experience from the comfort of your own home! Step outside to your backyard, complete with a covered patio and privacy fence, making it the perfect place to enjoy outdoor gatherings or simply relax. Don’t miss the opportunity to own this remarkable home! Contact us today to schedule your viewing!
